- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is also likely as the paper focuses on improving the performance of multiple string matching algorithms through parallelization on multicore CPUs. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possibility as the paper discusses a software implementation of the algorithm. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is another possibility as the paper discusses the implementation and evaluation of the algorithm. 
- cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the use of multicore CPUs for improving performance.
